      <title>BMO 称加拿大股市创纪录的涨势仍有空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/canadian-stocks-record-setting-rally-has-room-to-run-bmo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BMO 资本市场表示，得益于随时可用的散户现金储备和外国投资者的流入，加拿大股市有望在未来几个月继续创下纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/canadian-stocks-record-setting-rally-has-room-to-run-bmo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛和 Wren House 入围 Nabiax 拍卖会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/goldman-wren-house-are-said-to-be-shortlisted-in-nabiax-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，Nabiax 的所有者已经将包括高盛集团基础设施部门在内的多家公司列入候选名单，作为这家西班牙数据中心运营商的潜在买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/goldman-wren-house-are-said-to-be-shortlisted-in-nabiax-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:29:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>千禧年高级燃料交易员因能源团队变动而离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/millennium-senior-fuels-trader-leaves-amid-energy-team-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，随着该对冲基金大宗商品业务的发展，Millennium Management LLC 的高级燃料交易员和其他三名交易员即将离职，而 Castleton Commodities 的一名高级天然气交易员也将加入该对冲基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/millennium-senior-fuels-trader-leaves-amid-energy-team-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:19:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注降息路径，欧元飙升至一年高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/euro-surges-to-one-year-high-as-traders-eye-interest-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元兑美元升至一年来最高水平，因为货币交易员押注美国央行行长将在杰克逊霍尔美联储经济研讨会上强调降低借贷成本的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/euro-surges-to-one-year-high-as-traders-eye-interest-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:47:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据修正推动美联储降息预期，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/treasuries-gain-as-updated-us-data-fuels-bets-for-fed-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国修正就业数据增强了人们对美联储将于下个月开始降息的预期，美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/treasuries-gain-as-updated-us-data-fuels-bets-for-fed-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷将与美国签署协议以促进金属开采</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/argentina-to-join-us-group-for-spurring-metals-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院官员表示，阿根廷将与美国签署一项协议，以吸引更多关键矿产开采领域的投资和贸易，这是美国正在进行的加强不涉及中国的金属供应链的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/argentina-to-join-us-group-for-spurring-metals-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据延迟公布后，墨西哥比索领跌新兴市场货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/tech-stocks-china-drag-down-emerging-markets-as-rebound-stalls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥比索是周三新兴市场中跌幅最大的货币，因为数据显示美国就业增长远不如之前报告的强劲，该货币受到重挫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/tech-stocks-china-drag-down-emerging-markets-as-rebound-stalls</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:25:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：就业形势决定美联储降息 美国收益率下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
